<div class="calcpad-output">
 <!-- [Navier double-trig-series solution](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bending_of_plates#Bending_of_rectangular_plates) for a thin rectangular plate on simple supports under uniform load.
<p>Returns maximum deflection and bending moments $M_x$, $M_y$ for arbitrary plan dimensions, thickness and elastic constants — a quick parametric check against slab FEA. -->
 <h3>Input data</h3>
 <p>
  Dimensions in plan -
  <span class="eq">
